\doxysubsection{Detailed Description}
This class provides an empty implementation of \mbox{\hyperlink{interfaceit_1_1unical_1_1mat_1_1parsers_1_1datalog_1_1datalog__parser__base_1_1DatalogGrammarVisitor}{Datalog\+Grammar\+Visitor}}, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
